OL,3,C'Urgent investigation' started into
OL,4,CSark Electricity price hikes
OL,6,FSark's Government says the Electricity
OL,7,FPrice Control Commissioner has started
OL,8,Fan "urgent formal investigation" into
OL,9,Frecent fee hikes by the island's power
OL,10,Fcompany.
OL,12,FSark Electricity Limited will more
OL,13,Fthan double the existing unit cost
OL,14,Ffrom 49p to #1.14, with the higher
OL,15,Fcharge coming in from Monday 1
OL,16,FSeptember.
