OL,3,C'Urgent investigation' started into
OL,4,CSark Electricity price hikes
OL,6,FThe utility firm says the rise is
OL,7,Fneeded to cover legal costs to fight
OL,8,Fthe attempted compulsory purchase by
OL,9,FChief Pleas, but government officials
OL,10,Fhave called the move "unjustified".
OL,12,FIn a joint statement, the Committees
OL,13,Ffor Policy and Finance, and Future
OL,14,FEnergy say they are "extremely
OL,15,Fconcerned" and "recognise that a price
OL,16,Frise of this scale may cause financial
OL,17,Fhardship for many".
