OL,3,C'Urgent investigation' started into
OL,4,CSark Electricity price hikes
OL,6,FThey add: "In response, the
OL,7,FElectricity Price Control Commissioner
OL,8,Fhas launched an urgent formal
OL,9,Finvestigation into whether this new
OL,10,Fpricing is fair and reasonable; if the
OL,11,FCommissioner concludes that the
OL,12,Fincrease is not justified, a new Price
OL,13,FControl Order may be issued to set a
OL,14,Fregulated price."
OL,16,FA draft ruling by the independent
OL,17,Fcommissioner, Shane Lynch, is expected
OL,18,Fto be published early next week.
