OL,3,C'Urgent investigation' started into
OL,4,CSark Electricity price hikes
OL,6,FThis will be followed by a
OL,7,Fconsultation and then a final
OL,8,Fdecision, which is expected by the end
OL,9,Fof September.
OL,11,FThe Committees explain that if Sark
OL,12,FElectricity Limited "attempted to
OL,13,Fdisconnect large numbers of residents
OL,14,Ffor non-payment of unjustified bills,
OL,15,FChief Pleas would immediately seek the
OL,16,Fintervention of the Civil
OL,17,FContingencies Authority to ensure
OL,18,Fresidents are protected and that no
OL,19,Fone is placed at risk".
