OL,3,C'Urgent investigation' started into
OL,4,CSark Electricity price hikes
OL,6,FOn the compulsory purchase process,
OL,7,Fthe Committees say that a valuer has
OL,8,Fbeen suggested to Sark Electricity
OL,9,FLimited to agree on a fair price.
OL,11,FThey add: "If agreement cannot be
OL,12,Freached, the Policy and Finance
OL,13,FCommittee will apply to the Court for
OL,14,Fan order appointing the valuer in
OL,15,Faccordance with the statutory process."
OL,17,FCustomers who are concerned about how
OL,18,Fthey will pay their higher bills are
OL,19,Fasked to contact Sark Electricity
OL,20,FLimited first, but can also speak to
OL,21,Fthe Island Safeguarding Officer.
